data.description: This 5 bedroom 4.5 bath home is ready for a new family.  This home has been remodeled from top to bottom with granite countertops, new flooring and modern light fixtures.  You will love your kitchen with all of the custom cabinets, storage and all of the kitchen appliances will stay in the home.  There are 2 master suites and each of the suites have there own bathrooms with several walk in closets and a door that goes out to the patio.  There is another bedroom with a full bath and closets that can be accessed from the garage that can be used for an office, gym or mother in law quarters.  There is alot of storage throughout this home.  The backyard is spacious enough for you to add a pool.
